x4freetext: G-RAY PRODUCTION CROSS SECTION FOR INELASTIC SCATTERING
OF NEUTRONS OF THE FISSION SPECTRUM
THIS METHOD WAS DESCRIBED IN J,AE,20,143,1966 AND
30 MM IN DIAMETER AND 20 MM IN HEIGHT WAS USED
GAMMAS WERE DETECTED AT THE ANGLE 90 DEGREES

WERE 30-50 PERCENT IN CONTINIOUS RANGE AND LESS IN THE
RANGE OF THE SINGLE LINES.CORRECTION FOR MULTISCATTE-
